{"type":"message","id":"ab3a73c6","parentId":"d5d2a96a","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:03:21.973Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see:\n\n1. BE dashboard controller uses `countsMap` with keys like `total`, `tuitionDebt`, and status keys from DB\n2. FE uses `stats?.counts` and `statusKeys` — already aligned with `cbe45c6` fix\n\nThe BE has significant changes to the dashboard controller — it now uses the 4-collection notification model and returns `countsMap` with the status keys. The FE is already aligned with this (via `cbe45c6` fix which is in `feat/database-master`).\n\nSo the two branches are compatible and can be merged. The most logical approach:\n\n\n1. Merge BE `feat/notification-migration` into `origin/develop`\n2. Merge FE `feat/database-master` into `origin/develop`\n3. Then deploy both\n\nBut since the FE `cbe45c6` fix aligns with the BE dashboard changes, I need to check if the FE branch already includes this alignment or if it was done separately on the FE side. Looking at the commit history, `cbe45c6` is in `feat/database-master`, which means the FE branch already has the fix.\n\nNow I'm checking the `getDashboardStats` endpoint response structure to see if there are any API contract mismatches between the branches.","thinkingSignature":"bb559e46b0935f48df0a2921a954aa875d32c4794c8d07bd3b406e7b58422943"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p59nwbzaq6jw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be && grep -n \"sendSuccess\\|sendResponse\\|res.json\\|res.status\" src/interface/controllers/dashboard.controller.ts | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p59nwbzaq6jw_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe && git diff origin/develop..HEAD -- src/services/api.ts 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"^\\+.*url|^\\-.*url|\\.get\\(|\\.post\\(\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":487,"output":427,"cacheRead":45530,"cacheWrite":1549,"totalTokens":47993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776002590979,"responseId":"062ad91fec3c981a1299e47143aa0c83"}}
