 ahv-qlhv-be\n- Current branch: feat/notification-migration\n- Target: origin/develop\n- Label: ahv-qlhv:merge:be\n\n## Steps\n1. cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be\n2. Verify you're on feat/notification-migration: git branch --show-current\n3. git fetch origin develop\n4. Check for conflicts: git merge origin/develop --no-commit --no-ff\n5. If conflicts exist → list them and STOP\n6. If no conflicts:\n   a. Abort the test merge: git merge --abort\n   b. Create MR via GitLab API:\n      - Project ID: 81078323\n      - Source branch: feat/notification-migration\n      - Target branch: develop\n      - Title: \"feat(qlhv): notification migration Phase 3 + dashboard stats alignment\"\n      - Use gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request tool\n7. Report the MR URL and status\n\n## Rules\n- Never force push\n- If conflicts found → report exactly which files\n- Use gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request tool (NOT manual git push)","label":"ahv-qlhv:merge:be","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"senior-backend","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"mode":"run","cleanup":"delete"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_57wzri90ryy2_2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are senior-frontend. Merge the ahv-qlhv-fe branch into develop on GitLab.\n\n## Context\n- Workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup\n- Repo: ahv-qlhv-fe\n- Current branch: feat/database-master\n- Target: origin/develop\n- Label: ahv-qlhv:merge:fe\n\n## Steps\n1. cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe\n2. Verify you're on feat/database-master: git branch --show-current\n3. git fetch origin develop\n4. Check for conflicts: git merge origin/develop --no-commit --no-ff\n5. If conflicts exist → list them and STOP\n6. If no conflicts:\n   a. Abort the test merge: git merge --abort\n   b. Crea