{"type":"message","id":"95e95ace","parentId":"abe2ce48","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:35:58.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me compile the mandatory tasks for DTLX.\n\nKey findings:\n1. MR !166 - only open MR. 22 commits ahead of origin/develop, pipeline passed (268), can_be_merged. Ready for Lead approval.\n2. `optimization/conventions` - pipeline 269 passed, but no open MR visible (may need to check)\n3. All other branches have no MRs and CI failing\n4. DTLX FE - not cloned, no MRs\n\nMandatory tasks:\n1. **BE: Merge MR !166** - 22 commits ready to merge\n\n\n2. **FE: Clone & review** - FE hasn't been set up locally yet\n3. **BE: Create MRs for unmerged branches** - multiple branches are sitting without merge requests, which is risky\n4. **BE: Fix CI failures** - several branches have failing pipelines that need attention\n5. **BE: Sync develop into local** - while the local branch is current with origin/develop, there are 22 commits waiting to be merged upstream","thinkingSignature":"d9d482004b16a1e92646ef22e00abcccced2f26d9de97d1ddc95000388c3fa4e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔴 Nhiệm vụ BẮT BUỘC cho DTLX\n\n---\n\n### 🖥️ DTLX Backend — 6 nhiệm vụ\n\n**1. 🔴 Merge MR !166 ngay — 22 commits đang chờ**\n- URL: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/merge_requests/166\n- Trạng thái: ✅ Pipeline passed (id: 2416854588) | ✅ Can merge\n- Nội dung: Restructure routes → presentation/api layer (Phase 1 clean architecture)\n- Tác giả: Lead (khuowgn) | Reviewer: Hiếu\n- ⚠️ **Cần Lead approve & merge thủ công**\n\n**2. 🔴 Tạo MR cho `optimization/conventions`**\n- Commit: `3d125b1f` — implement prettier cho repository\n- Pipeline: ✅ Passed (id: 2416857386)\n- Nhưng **không có MR** → cần tạo\n\n**3. 🔴 Tạo MR cho `fix/build-operability-and-typos`**\n- Chứa restore developer fix cho imports.controller.ts\n- Pipeline: ❌ **Failed** → cần fix trước khi merge\n\n**4. 🔴 Review hotfix branches — CI đang fail**\n\n| Branch | Nội dung | CI | Cần |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `hotfix/import-student` | Fix import | ❌ Fail | Fix + MR |\n| `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc` | NFC Unicode fix | ✅ Passed (đã merge vào production) | Merge vào develop |\n| `refactor/antigravity` | Fix model overwrite + mongoose | ❌ Fail | Fix + MR |\n| `refactor/split-app-server` | Separate app/server init | ❌ Fail | Fix + MR |\n| `refactor/merge-api-common` | Merge API common | ❌ Fail | Fix + MR |\n\n**5. 🟡 Sync `develop` → `refactor/main` sau khi merge Phase 1**\n- Sau khi !166 merge, `refactor/main` cần sync lại với `develop` mới nhất\n- Nhiều commit đã merged vào develop sau khi Phase 1 tách ra\n\n**6. 🟡 Production hotfix cần forward-port**\n- Unicode NFC fix (đã merge production) → cần merge vào develop\n\n---\n\n### 🖥️ DTLX Frontend — 2 nhiệm vụ\n\n**7. 🔴 Clone & setup local**\n- Project: `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend` (ID: 77055851)\n- Last activity: Apr 7, 2026 — stale ~6 ngày\n- Không có MR nào đang mở\n- Cần Lead chỉ định task tiếp theo\n\n**8. 🟡 Review FE code — có thay đổi gì đang chờ?**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Tổng hợp — Thứ tự ưu tiên\n\n```\n1. [Lead] Approve & merge MR !166         ← Chỉ Lead làm được\n2. [Orbis] Tạo MR optimization/conventions\n3. [Orbis] Fix CI fix/build-operability-and-typos\n4. [Orbis] Fix CI hotfix/import-student\n5. [Orbis] Fix CI refactor/antigravity\n6. [Orbis] Fix CI refactor/split-app-server\n7. [Orbis] Fix CI refactor/merge-api-common\n8. [Orbis] Clone DTLX FE\n```\n\nLead muốn Orbis xử lý từ bước nào?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1319,"output":1073,"cacheRead":76750,"cacheWrite":7539,"totalTokens":86681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776069321934,"responseId":"062bddcbd436fa87a71d0d15d73e362a"}}
