{"type":"message","id":"4a156fc5","parentId":"d277eb0d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:46:52.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the previous agent is killed. Now let me start with Module 1: AUTH. I'll spawn senior-backend to test auth endpoints first.","thinkingSignature":"363cef4c16e62fc6f0623f6afc6766184fd6f74fd310ce720daefaf09c4248d7"},{"type":"text","text":"Đã kill agent cũ. Bắt đầu **Module 1: AUTH** (public endpoints).\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6z6ewsa6dqc8_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are senior-backend. Test Module 1: AUTH API for ahv-dtlx-backend.\n\n## Context\n- Workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- Server port: 5555\n- Label: dtlx:auth-test\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Setup\n- cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- cp .env.example .env  (if .env doesn't exist)\n- Run: yarn seed  (seeds admin account admin123@gmail.com / 123456)\n- Start server: yarn dev  (background)\n- Wait for server to start (look for \"listening\" or \"started\")\n\n### 2. Test AUTH endpoints (PUBLIC - no token needed)\nUse curl to test each endpoint:\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/auth/login\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\", \"password\": \"123456\" }\nExpected: JWT token\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/register  \nBody: { \"email\": \"test@test.com\", \"password\": \"123456\", \"name\": \"Test User\" }\nExpected: user created\n\nGET /api/v1/auth/me\nExpected: current user info (if authenticated)\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\" }\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/refresh\n```\n\n### 3. After login success\n- Save the JWT token from login response\n- Test GET /api/v1/auth/me with the token (Authorization: Bearer <token>)\n\n### 4. Report\nFor EACH endpoint, report:\n- ✅ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, response (truncated if long)\n- ❌ /api/v1/auth/xxx — HTTP status, error message\n\n## Rules\n- Read-only API testing\n- NEVER push or commit code\n- Kill background server when done","label":"dtlx:module1-auth","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"senior-backend","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"mode":"run","cleanup":"delete"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":285,"output":592,"cacheRead":91559,"cacheWrite":83,"totalTokens":92519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776131198281,"responseId":"062ccf80ed891bb37895a178fb5db03f"}}
