{"type":"message","id":"566f531d","parentId":"b18aa034","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:56:56.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the issue is that the **services** are returning `{ docs, meta }` but the **interfaces** now expect `{ data, meta }`. I updated the interfaces but not the services. The cleanest approach is to also update the services to return `{ data, meta }` instead of `{ docs, meta }`.\n\nThere are many services to update. Let me write a comprehensive script to fix all of them.\n\nFiles with issues:\n1. `courses.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n2. `devices.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n3. `exams.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n\n\n4. `internalCosts.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n5. `leadSources.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }` (also missing `totalPages`)\n6. `lessons.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n7. `notifyConfigs.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n8. `studentInfos.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n9. `teacherInfos.service.ts` - returns `{ data, meta }` (already fixed)\n10. `users.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n11. `workCalendars.service.ts` - returns `{ docs, meta }`\n\nI need to systematically update each service to return the correct structure with `{ data, meta }` instead of `{ docs, meta }`.","thinkingSignature":"174049efa269d398028af68969d889fec72e6633a85a6f9a2b47730ecdf2eb07"},{"type":"text","text":"Services vẫn return `{ docs, meta }`. Fix tất cả service files.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l1vvtz8x2qxl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend && python3 -c \"\nimport re\n\nfiles = [\n    'src/modules/courses/courses.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/devices/devices.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/exams/exams.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/internalCosts/internalCosts.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/lessons/lessons.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/notifyConfigs/notifyConfigs.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/studentInfos/studentInfos.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/users/users.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/workCalendars/workCalendars.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/teacherInfos/teacherInfos.service.ts',\n    'src/modules/leadSources/leadSources.service.ts',\n]\n\nfor f in files:\n    with open(f) as fh:\n        content = fh.read()\n    # Replace return { docs: ..., meta: ... } with return { data: ..., meta: ... }\n    # Pattern: 'return { docs:' followed by content, closing with '};'\n    new_content = re.sub(\n        r'return \\{ docs: ([^,]+), meta: ([^}]+) \\}',\n        r'return { data: \\1, meta: \\2 }',\n        content\n    )\n    # Also handle destructured: return { docs: data, meta }\n    new_content = re.sub(\n        r'return \\{ docs: data, meta \\}',\n        r'return { data: data, meta }',\n        new_content\n    )\n    if new_content != content:\n        with open(f, 'w') as fh:\n            fh.write(new_content)\n        print(f'Fixed: {f}')\n    else:\n        print(f'No change: {f}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":3158,"output":715,"cacheRead":117035,"cacheWrite":283,"totalTokens":121191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776135394557,"responseId":"062cdfe47f9f8053e366ea9442ac8a15"}}
